snippet.title: TS4 Extreme Violence MOD - V1.7 Gangs Trailer
snippet.description:
Populate the town with brutal gangs or join one yourself! The Thotties & The HardWood, fight against them or alley with them in their brutal crimes.

Read full release notes here:
http://www.sacrificialmods.com/extreme-violence-news.html

Download the mod from here:
http://sims4studio.com/post/76154 

The thotties theme song: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yql3r_6c2EA

The HardWood Theme Song: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FQ9uZOz0KBw Trap by lab Vol.1 - Hard Trap Beat Instrumental #5 (Prod. Labaneh B)
